title: Kyte v1.1.9 - Flat Onepage Responsive WordPress Theme
description:
Kyte is a flat, responsive, WordPress Theme built with Twitter Bootstrap with unique portfolio. It can be used both as onepage and multipage. Kyte will be useful to artists, photographers, creative agencies, digital studios, personal freelancers, and any kind of business owners that would like to showcase their portfolio beautifully. Since it is responsive, the layout will adapt to different screen sizes which will make your website be compatible with any device such as smart phones, tablets or desktop computers. 4 premium scripts are included with the total value of $65, which you will get for free with this theme.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/kyte-flat-onepage-responsive-wordpress-theme/5540844

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
